{"tid":2349400,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"國產製Cyberpunk風格RPG《紀元變異》延期","createTime":"2021-01-01T14:01:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T21:42:54.000Z","uid":36122,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"7473f58be95b359a36eb27151fe2ab527e0a564c","tid":2349400,"uid":36122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:01:41.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪因為&lt;Cyberbug 2077&gt; 搞唔掂無得抄呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n作為Sony「中國之星計畫」的一員，《紀元變異》原定於今年12月在PlayStation平台發佈。該作的PC版也將於2021年推出，不久前還在Steam平台推出了試玩Demo。<br />\n<br />\n開發團隊表示，遊戲之所以延期，是因為他們「決定將遊戲的整體體驗進行全面升級，這代表著大量的遊戲內容必須重新規劃並推倒重做」，「為了適應已經到來的次時代主機平台和玩家們，我們希望在遊戲發佈時給大家一個更加飽滿的劇情體驗」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202012/29/e9ed23887020a237.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202012%2F29%2Fe9ed23887020a237.jpg&h=0b68b4f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://image.gameapps.hk/images/202012/29/4e78a460b24c6c5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.gameapps.hk%2Fimages%2F202012%2F29%2F4e78a460b24c6c5d.jpg&h=79a4281e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameapps.hk/news/42736/cyberpunk-rpg-delag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameapps.hk%2Fnews%2F42736%2Fcyberpunk-rpg-delag&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gYICM%2BRBTk%2Byah4LEbU4uIE%3D&h=965ca00e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameapps.hk/news/42736/cyberpunk-rpg-delag</a>"},{"pid":"5e8a1d2224c5cbf648ae9cae8353c659d810894d","tid":2349400,"uid":3341,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"連delay都抄足<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgm